EN: We hope you can take over this position.

ZH: 这个公司正在寻找一个新的CEO来接手。
EN: The company is looking for a new CEO to take over.

ZH: 父亲突然生病了，我不得不接手他的生意。
EN: My father suddenly got sick, and I had to take over his business.

